OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776445554
OL,3,CStill no date for delayed hospital
OL,4,Copenings
OL,6,FThe new maternity and children's
OL,7,Fhospitals on the Royal Victoria site
OL,8,Fhave been plagued with delays for
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FOn Thursday afternoon, the Health
OL,12,FCommittee heard from the management of
OL,13,Fthe Belfast Trust and were told that
OL,14,Fthere is still no date for when either
OL,15,Fof the two new hospitals will open
OL,16,Ftheir doors.
OL,18,FThe Children's hospital was due to
OL,19,Fopen in 2020, six years go but
OL,20,Fconstruction only started last year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776445554
OL,3,CStill no date for delayed hospital
OL,4,Copenings
OL,6,FDifficulties with the water system are
OL,7,Fcreating more set backs.
OL,9,FDavid Porter, Belfast Trust said: "It
OL,10,Fwill have an impact on cost and
OL,11,Fprogram. But the trust have not yet
OL,12,Freceived that information through from
OL,13,Fthe contractor and so on."
OL,15,FIt's not only the the children's
OL,16,Fhospital, the nearby maternity
OL,17,Fhospital was due to open over a decade
OL,18,Fago but was delayed due to the
OL,19,Fbacteria Pseudomonas aeruginosa found
OL,20,Fin the waterpipes.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776445554
OL,3,CStill no date for delayed hospital
OL,4,Copenings
OL,6,FJennifer Welsh, Belfast Trust Chief
OL,7,FExecutive said: "We are as frustrated
OL,8,Fas you are in relation to everything
OL,9,Fthat has that has occurred.
OL,11,F"We very much want to be able to get
OL,12,Fthis building open and in service to
OL,13,Fthe people that need it.
OL,15,F"But also for our staff who have
OL,16,Fworked incredibly hard and hoped that
OL,17,Fthey obviously would have been been
OL,18,Fdelivering babies in this unit at at
OL,19,Fthis stage."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
