OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776445554
OL,3,CStill no date for delayed hospital
OL,4,Copenings
OL,6,FTo solve the problem, the pipes are
OL,7,Fhaving to be flushed out. But
OL,8,Fquestions were raised on Thursday,
OL,9,Fwhether or not it will fix the issue.
OL,11,FDiane Dodds, MLA DUP asked: "What
OL,12,Fmakes you think that flushing the
OL,13,Fpipework for another two years will
OL,14,Fget rid of the Pseudomonas in the main
OL,15,Fmaternity hospital, not the neonatal
OL,16,Fpart of it, when it hasn't done it in
OL,17,Fthe last two years?"
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776445554
OL,3,CStill no date for delayed hospital
OL,4,Copenings
OL,6,FDavid Porter, Belfast Trust responded:
OL,7,F"We are doing more than that as part
OL,8,Fof the remediation works for the
OL,9,Fremainder of the building.
OL,11,F"So we are removing any of the outlets
OL,12,Fthat have tested positive for
OL,13,FPseudomonas.
OL,15,F"We are replacing some of the valves
OL,16,Fas well which were considered to be a
OL,17,Frisk.
OL,19,F"So there are more works than that
OL,20,Fthat are involved as part of the
OL,21,Fremediation works.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776445554
OL,3,CStill no date for delayed hospital
OL,4,Copenings
OL,6,F"And the advice that we're getting
OL,7,Ffrom our experts is that following the
OL,8,Fremediation works, following that
OL,9,Fmitigation work, that the system
OL,10,Fshould be able to deliver safe potable
OL,11,Fwater within the building.
OL,13,F"So our caution in all of that is of
OL,14,Fcourse to say that we cannot give that
OL,15,Fas an absolute guarantee as I've
OL,16,Fmentioned.
OL,18,F"But we do have a level of confidence
OL,19,Fin what we're doing moving forward."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
